点、特产等，让您在虚拟体验中了解仓吉的魅力。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[#nanashikurayoshi] VTuber 女孩之旅！与Hikari Hira一起游览鸟取县仓吉市的11家推荐观光和美食餐厅[泉柚原/七新久]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OBxXyS4e-0E?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> VTuber团体“ <a href="https://www.774.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nanashi Think</a> ”的<a href="https://twitter.com/Izumi_Yunohara" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>柚原泉</strong></a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/Hikari_Hira" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Hikari</strong></a> Hira公开了仓吉当地旅游视频“ <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OBxXyS4e-0E" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nanashi仓吉友谊之旅</a>”。这是仓吉市实际旅行的视频，介绍仓吉市的推荐观光景点以及当地美食的魅力。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/dbe55dbfd3fafee3bb19299924db0344-kix.swz80b3d0kme-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/dbe55dbfd3fafee3bb19299924db0344-kix.swz80b3d0kme-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/dbe55dbfd3fafee3bb19299924db0344-kix.swz80b3d0kme-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/dbe55dbfd3fafee3bb19299924db0344-kix.swz80b3d0kme-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/dbe55dbfd3fafee3bb19299924db0344-kix.swz80b3d0kme-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/dbe55dbfd3fafee3bb19299924db0344-kix.swz80b3d0kme-jpg.webp 1148w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/dbe55dbfd3fafee3bb19299924db0344-kix.wj23feip1aw6-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/dbe55dbfd3fafee3bb19299924db0344-kix.wj23feip1